<div class="article-1">
<h1 class="article">Supreme Court Looks Poised To Invalidate A Major Penal Program</h1> <p class="byline">
Posted at 3:30 pm on February 27, 2019 by <a href="/streiff">streiff</a>
</p>
<div class="row button-span">
<div class="col-xs-9">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-6 sc">
<button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-lg sc-fb fb"><span class="icon-fa-facebook-official"></span>Share on Facebook<span class="fb-count"></span></button>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-6">
<button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-lg sc-tw tw btn-block"><span class="icon-fa-twitter"></span>Share on Twitter</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-3">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-4">
<button type="button" onclick="window.print()" class="btn btn-default btn-lg btn-block"><span class="icon-fa-print"></span></button>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-4">
<a href="javascript:;" data-enc-email="?fhowrpg=Erqubg&obql=Fhcerzr Pbheg Ybbxf Cbvfrq Gb Vainyvqngr N Znwbe Crany Cebtenzuggcf://jjj.erqfgngr.pbz/fgervss/2019/02/27/fhcerzr-pbheg-ybbxf-cbvfrq-vainyvqngr-znwbe-crany-cebtenz/" class="mail-link" data-wpel-link="ignore">
<button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-lg btn-block">
<span class="icon-fa-envelope"></span>
</button>
</a>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-4">
<a href="#disqus-comments">
<button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-lg btn-block"><span class="icon-fa-comment"></span></button>
